overview: Les Delices du Tossing (literally translates to "The Delights of Tossing"), the 1983 Gerard Kikoine French sexploitation movie starring Cathy Stewart, Patricia Samba, Christine Schwarz, Marianne Aubert, Marilyn Jess, and Alban Ceray. It appears this movie was never released in the U.S.
title: Les Délices du tossing
